description.en:
Shibcake is the most rewarded cake reflection token.


Each person who holds more than 200,000 tokens will receive automatically a number of Cake tokens, the governance token of Pancakeswap.


On each transaction, 20% fees are applied for buyers and 21% for the sellers.

- 15% are redistributed in CAKE to the holders.

- 1% for the liquidity.

- 4% to the marketing wallet

- 1% extra fee on sell orders
